			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1408809">
									

<p>I pick them up here and there, wherever and whenever i see something unsettling, creepy, or odd. The hope is, at some point, they'll inspire me, or fit an idea i have, somehow. I also think it's odd that mummified zombies haven't been explored more in fiction. Yes, they'd probably be more stiff and such, but if you're going to have the dead walk, they may as well shuffle too.</p>
<p>It's the old woman's expression that gets me in this picture. There's this&#8230;resignation in it that is kind of compelling.</p>

